Welcome

Thank you for visiting the St. Paul's Baptist Church of Conshohocken online ministry. We are a bible believing church. We strive to enrich the spiritual growth of it's members and the community.

As a church family, we are trying to become the kind of church described in the Bible, where there is relevant teaching, heart-felt worship, honest friendships, constant prayer and compassionate care for those in need. We would like to have a contagious faith that will influence and encourage our entire community, one life at a time.

Our church doors are wide open to people of all backgrounds regardless of where they are on their spiritual journey. So whether you are a spiritual seeker who is just starting to ask questions about God and faith, or a committed Christian who wants to sink the roots of your faith even deeper, you can find a home here at St. Paul's Baptist Church of Conshohocken.

Thank you and have a blessed day.

Pastoral Search Committee

It is with great joy that the Pastoral Search Committee has good news. After a long, prayerful and careful search, we’re excited to present Reverend Dr. Marjorie Duncan Reed as the candidate for the pastoral position of our church.

See a biographical summary of Reverend Dr. Marjorie Duncan Reed, the candidate who is being recommended.

Reverend Dr. Reed will be preaching on the second Sunday February 9th and the third Sunday February 16th 2014 at the 10:30AM worship services. Please be in prayer for this affirmation of GOD's plan.

In HIS spirit,

The Pastoral Search Committee

Church School

Please come out to join us for our church school program every Sunday, beginning at 9 am.  There is a class for all ages!  It is a great time to learn more about our Lord and to have great discussions about His word.  We hope to see you there!



St. Paul's Baptist Church, Conshohocken Pennsylvania
